; Test account-rewrite directive
; Exercise the account_rewrite_mappings flow
; The account is replaced with the substitution pattern

account-rewrite Food  Groceries

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg
24-Jan-01 Test                  Groceries                    $10.00       $10.00
24-Jan-01 Test                  Assets:Cash                 $-10.00            0
end test
